OL,3,CVatican says Pope health in critical
OL,4,Ccondition
OL,6,FThe Vatican has described the Pope's
OL,7,Fcondition for the first time as
OL,8,F"critical" as he remains in hospital
OL,9,Fwith a complex lung infection. ITV
OL,10,FNews' Ellie Pitt reports from Rome
OL,12,FPope Francis is in a critical
OL,13,Fcondition after he suffered a long
OL,14,Fasthmatic respiratory crisis that
OL,15,Frequired high flows of oxygen, The
OL,16,FVatican says.
