OL,6,FThe 88-year-old, who has been
OL,7,Fhospitalised at Rome's Gemelli
OL,8,Fhospital for a week with a complex
OL,9,Flung infection, also received blood
OL,10,Ftransfusions after tests showed a
OL,11,Fcondition associated with anemia, the
OL,12,FVatican said in a late update.
OL,14,F"The Holy Father continues to be alert
OL,15,Fand spent the day in an armchair
OL,16,Falthough in more pain than yesterday.
OL,18,F"At the moment the prognosis is
OL,19,Freserved," the statement said.
