OL,3,CVatican says Pope health in critical
OL,4,Ccondition
OL,6,FThe latest update from the Vatican
OL,7,Fcomes just one day after his medical
OL,8,Fteam's first public news conference
OL,9,Fwhich said his condition was not life-
OL,10,Fthreatening but that he was also "not
OL,11,Fout of danger."
OL,13,FOn Friday, Dr. Luigi Carbone said:
OL,14,F"like all fragile patients I say they
OL,15,Fare always on the golden scale: In
OL,16,Fother words, it takes very little to
OL,17,Fbecome unbalanced."
OL,19,FDoctors said Francis would remain in
OL,20,Fhospital for at least another week.
